content:
Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.

Einstein Discovery allows you to:

* Build Models in Einstein Discovery
* Manage and Deploy Models in Einstein Discovery
* Evaluate Model Quality
* Compare Models
* Deploy Models

Distribute Prediction Definitions and Models with Managed and Unmanaged Packages. You can build and train models using your own data, then distribute them within or outside your company.

To add prediction definitions and models to a package:

* Create a package in Package Manager.
* Click Add Component and select Analytics Model, Analytics Model Configuration, or Analytics Model Prediction Definition.
* Select one or more models or prediction definitions.
* Click Add Component

Managed packages are supported through First-Generation Managed Packages and Second-Generation Managed Packages.

Decision Optimization (Beta) is available.
title: Packaging and Distributing Prediction Definitions and Models
